CHOLERA - GHANA (03)
********************
A ProMED-mail post
See Also

Date: Fri, 06 Feb 1998 08:12:53 +0000
From: Steve Berger <mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

The following data on cholera in Uganda were abstracted from the GIDEON
software program:
Year Cases Fatal
1982 190
1987 140
1991 279 28
1992 5,072 104
1993 0
1994 704 39
1995 538 66
1996 291 40
1997 370 29
In recent years, activity had been limited to Kasase District. During
December 1997, 70 cases (3 fatal) were
confirmed in Kampala City and 26 cholera deaths were reported in Bugiri
District (Busoga Province).
--
Dr. Steve Berger
e-mail: mberger@post.tau.ac.il
